<plot>In 2004, the Edinburgh Festival sees the world premier of the film Dead Man's Shoes from Midlands director Shane Meadows. In this short documentary Meadows takes us from the inspiration for the film, indeed the very event that he feels turned him into the person he is today, and the actual making of his fourth feature film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262245</url></doc>
